title: 2025 start.
content: 2025 will truly be a year of making the most of what i have. the foundation that i have built up will come to life. my dreams shall become reality.

title: identity.
content:
identity affects ability

  • if our identity is limited by a weak foundation, we won’t be able to achieve anything more than it.
  • high self-esteem and secure identity correlates with overcoming goals
  • “who am i?” must be answered before “what do i want to do or be?”

many give up on their goals early in the year solely because of how they see themselves.

anything is achievable.
